item.dc:creator: ramak
item.content:encoded:
2017

YEAR IN REVIEW

2017 was a year of productivity and lots of fun. We explored new verticals, added new team members and consumed more caffeine than ever! Plus, we contributed in the every major update of WordPress that was released in 2017. So in honor of this momentous year, were offering an awesome free plugin and a full report on all things we did in 2017.

18

Plugins Launched

522,934

Product Downloads

18,622

New Customers Acquired

54

Client Projects Delivered

124

Countries where our customers are located Code Commits Support Team Members Tickets Resolved Proposals Komal got in support tickets Team Outings Walls Painted

And...

Lots of Fun!

2018

We want to thank you, our users, for being a part of it. Just wait till you see whats planned for 2018!
